# Service Layer

The application uses a service layer pattern to interact with the Supabase backend:

## Key Services
- [src/services/auth.ts](mdc:src/services/auth.ts) - Authentication and user management
- [src/services/groups.ts](mdc:src/services/groups.ts) - Group creation and management
- [src/services/expenses.ts](mdc:src/services/expenses.ts) - Expense tracking functions
- [src/services/expense_participants.ts](mdc:src/services/expense_participants.ts) - Managing expense splits
- [src/services/payments.ts](mdc:src/services/payments.ts) - Payment and settlement functions
- [src/services/users.ts](mdc:src/services/users.ts) - User profile operations
- [src/services/group_members.ts](mdc:src/services/group_members.ts) - Group membership functions

## Database Connection
Database connection is managed through [src/lib/supabase.ts](mdc:src/lib/supabase.ts)
